### <samp>🤖 Generated by Copilot at 1a7f386</samp>

* Fix typo in `Rearrange` UI text in `Gallery` component ([link](https://github.com/heyxyz/hey/pull/3930/files?diff=unified&w=0#diff-a3763e0db220dfddce1714efa5f222ceac5b6cf332fbc678c702765b18f1d3b1L215-R215))
* Update message IDs and strings for `Rearrange` in English translation file ([link](https://github.com/heyxyz/hey/pull/3930/files?diff=unified&w=0#diff-a91393d1e62c7dd6f423054d58557fdef61bb5a84cc28248690ad03e1b160365R1645-R1648), [link](https://github.com/heyxyz/hey/pull/3930/files?diff=unified&w=0#diff-a91393d1e62c7dd6f423054d58557fdef61bb5a84cc28248690ad03e1b160365L1657-R1662))
* Comment out unused message IDs and strings for `Rearrrange` in French, Russian, Tamil, and Chinese translation files ([link](https://github.com/heyxyz/hey/pull/3930/files?diff=unified&w=0#diff-e6e55bf08ac014b03ae04b5978c2232855f354712cd50cfe8942a7d6c84635d6R1645-R1648), [link](https://github.com/heyxyz/hey/pull/3930/files?diff=unified&w=0#diff-e53d289af6055d499884e2a85fd1686e0115f12d3a623db33ec92daf6c1ee7feR1645-R1648), [link](https://github.com/heyxyz/hey/pull/3930/files?diff=unified&w=0#diff-74c63dfeab2412f39f5a30f665845db007129732f3c107216bfb25faa66e3a48R1645-R1648), [link](https://github.com/heyxyz/hey/pull/3930/files?diff=unified&w=0#diff-be3912a3e9938530b5702e29149c1ee5dc96cd68c54b3691dd9d5eb225630ccdR1645-R1648))
* Update message IDs for `Rearrange` in French, Russian, Tamil, and Chinese translation files, leaving message strings blank for future translation updates ([link](https://github.com/heyxyz/hey/pull/3930/files?diff=unified&w=0#diff-e6e55bf08ac014b03ae04b5978c2232855f354712cd50cfe8942a7d6c84635d6L1657-R1661), [link](https://github.com/heyxyz/hey/pull/3930/files?diff=unified&w=0#diff-e53d289af6055d499884e2a85fd1686e0115f12d3a623db33ec92daf6c1ee7feL1657-R1662), [link](https://github.com/heyxyz/hey/pull/3930/files?diff=unified&w=0#diff-74c63dfeab2412f39f5a30f665845db007129732f3c107216bfb25faa66e3a48L1657-R1662), [link](https://github.com/heyxyz/hey/pull/3930/files?diff=unified&w=0#diff-be3912a3e9938530b5702e29149c1ee5dc96cd68c54b3691dd9d5eb225630ccdL1657-R1662))

issue.title: Incorrect detection of URL with semicolon
issue.body:
### Is there an existing issue for this?

- [X] I have searched the existing issues


### Steps To Reproduce

Create a post with an URL that contains a semicolon, for example:
```https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?action=profile;u=3```

### Current Behavior

Only a part of the URL is detected. See screenshots.

### Expected Behavior

The whole URL should be detected



### What platform(s) does this occur on?

Web

### What browser(s) does this occur on?

Chrome

### Anything else?

**Composing:**

![Screenshot_2023-10-23_19-41-52](https://github.com/heyxyz/hey/assets/667227/abd9baa8-62bf-439f-8b78-5a2a7850e9bc)


**Rendered:**

![Screenshot_2023-10-23_19-42-23](https://github.com/heyxyz/hey/assets/667227/876d902c-3e2e-4c04-b1e9-55b34b6944a7)
